Emergency rescue operations in the capital have been completed. It is known about 10 victims, including a 16-year-old girl. Two people were hospitalized.

About thisinformsMinistry of Internal Affairs of Ukraine.

In addition, the department noted that 25 people received psychological assistance from psychologists of the State Emergency Service.

"Information on the possible stay under the rubble of one person was not confirmed," - said in the Ministry of Internal Affairs.

As it is noted, more than 580 cubic meters were taken out. m building structures.
